(7, 0, 0, 50, '联系我们', '{cmspath}/about', 1, 'index.html', 1, 17, -1, 1, 0, '{style}/index_aboutus.htm', '{style}/list_aboutus.htm', '{style}/article_aboutus.htm', '{typedir}/{aid}.html', '{typedir}/{page}.html', 'default', '', '', '', 0, '{cmspath}/about', '', 0, 0, '', '&nbsp;', ''),
(8, 7, 7, 50, '关于我们', '{cmspath}/about', 1, 'index.html', 1, 17, -1, 0, 0, '{style}/index_aboutus.htm', '{style}/list_aboutus.htm', '{style}/article_aboutus.htm', '{typedir}/{aid}.html', '{typedir}/index.html', 'default', '', '', '', 0, '{cmspath}/about', '', 0, 0, '', '<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<p style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, Arial, Tahoma, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif;">\r\n		<span style="color:#000000;">本站于2011年12月31日正式上线，是科技资讯媒体。本站经过长期积淀，与多家知名媒体达成深度合作关系，现已成为百度、360、搜狗等多家新闻源。并拥有专栏作家六十余名，曾成功支持国内外多场互联网盛会并给予专业化报导。</span></p>\r\n	<p style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, Arial, Tahoma, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif;">\r\n		<span style="color:#000000;">本站媒体在团队、内容、渠道和版面上逐步转型，以独特视角把脉创业经济，推广展示创新产品、团队、事件、商业模式等，同时为创业企业、明星团队提供在线扶持，致力于打造成关注创新创业的高新科技媒体。</span></p>\r\n	<p style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, Arial, Tahoma, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif;">\r\n		<span style="color:#000000;">本站后期将联合国内外各地知名创业孵化机构、咖啡馆，实现创业资讯的新鲜传递，保证创业资讯第一手资料。并联合自身的庞大媒体资源与一微米创业平台</span><span style="color:#000000;">、同道会企业共同帮扶国内创业企业，助力创业经济。</span></p>\r\n	<p style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, Arial, Tahoma, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif;">\r\n		<span style="color:#000000;">本站将逐步转型，打造成致力于关注创新创业的高新科技媒体，以独特视角把脉创业经济，展现创业企业展示创新产品推荐、团队（人物）、事件（投融资事件分析）、服务（扶持计划）、商业模式探究； 本站将为参加活动的企业、一微米平台企业、同道会企业等提供宣传渠道。现在本站从团队、内容、渠道和版面方面都在改版，恳请各位同仁相互监督。</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n', ''),
(9, 7, 7, 50, '加入我们', '{cmspath}/joinus', 1, 'index.html', 1, 17, -1, 0, 0, '{style}/index_aboutus.htm', '{style}/list_aboutus.htm', '{style}/article_aboutus.htm', '{typedir}/{aid}.html', '{typedir}/index.html', 'default', '', '', '', 0, '{cmspath}/about', '', 0, 0, '', '<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	本站是一个正在发育中的创业公司，各方面条件待遇没法跟成熟大公司比。但我们团队将以最大诚意来欢迎与拥抱那些即将加入我们的年轻人！本站虽小，但是是公司良民，五险一金全都有。至于具体待遇，面议。你们也知道，我们相互的选择，是为了明天的而不是今天的什么！</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	以下是各个空缺岗位具体职责与要求，有意者请详阅，并发简历、相应作品及个人阐述至：884358@qq.com。</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	对进一步面试者，我们会在24小时内给予回复。其他简历，恕不一一回复了。</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	========================<span style="word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em;">=======</span><b style="word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em;"><font size="5" style="word-wrap: break-word;">产品设计</font></b><span style="word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em;">========================</span><span style="word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em;">=======</span></div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<font size="4" style="word-wrap: break-word;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">产品经理(1名)</b></font></div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	工作职责:</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	1、负责本站新产品的规划、设计，以及现有产品的优化</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	2、分析产品运营数据,不断完善和优化产品,提升产品的用户体验</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	3、确定开发计划,与团队密切配合,协调项目资源,跟踪项目进度,以顺利完成项目并达成目标</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	职位要求:</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	1、熟悉互联网,熟悉信息传播,具有敏锐的嗅觉，对互联网热门产品和服务有一定的洞察力和见解</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	2、具有优秀的计划能力、组织能力和执行能力,能够推动整个团队朝预定的目标快速前进</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	3、有较强的学习创新能力,逻辑思维能力,责任心强,具有良好的沟通能力和团队合作意识</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	4、注重用户交互体验者或3年以上的互联网产品经理相关经验者优先考虑</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	-----------------------------------------------------------<span style="word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em;">----------------------------------------------------</span><span style="word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em;">-------</span></div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<b style="word-wrap: break-word;"><font size="4" style="word-wrap: break-word;">网页设计师(1名)</font></b></div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	工作职责：</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	1、负责网站页面设计与UI交互</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	2、负责移动产品UI设计</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	3、负责内容、推广与运营的相关设计</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	职位要求：</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	1、人机交互、工业设计、视觉设计相关专业</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	2、了解Css、Javascript、Html等网络技术</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	3、优秀的GUI、UI界面及交互设计能力，对以人为本的设计理念有深入的理解</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	4、有大型资讯类网站Web界面、移动终端设计领域相关工作经验，对产品流程、用户交互流程及用户需求有深入理解</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	5、认真细致，善于创新，对视觉设计追求极致化，敏锐色彩感觉，及出色的观察与产品界面分析能力</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	========================<span style="word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em;">=======</span><b style="word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em;"><font size="5" style="word-wrap: break-word;">技术研发</font></b><span style="word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em;">=</span><span style="word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em;">=======</span><span style="word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em;">=======================</span></div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<b style="word-wrap: break-word;"><font size="4" style="word-wrap: break-word;">系统研发工程师(2名)</font></b></div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	工作职责：&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	1、参与高并发的后台处理系统的需求整理和开发工作</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	2、负责系统功能开发及性能优化、改进</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	3、编写、分析并优化新的算法或数据结构</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: