rd-wrap: break-word;"><font size="4" style="word-wrap: break-word;">运营推广（1名）</font></b></div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	工作职责：</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	1、负责包括微博在内的&mdash;&mdash;本站网站外的内容渠道与阵地的内容呈现与推广。</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	2、负责本站的UGC内容运营。</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	3、参与线下活动组织与推广。</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	职位要求：</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	1、对人对事皆敏感，喜欢发现，喜欢交流；能洞察用户心理需求，并以合适的内容满足之。</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	2、勤奋、自我驱动。能承受琐碎与重复的工作，甘当幕后功臣。</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	3、熟悉网络社区表达，思维活泼。</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	4、团队精神。</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n', ''),
(10, 7, 7, 50, '广告及服务', '{cmspath}/ad', 1, 'index.html', 1, 17, -1, 0, 0, '{style}/index_aboutus.htm', '{style}/list_aboutus.htm', '{style}/article_aboutus.htm', '{typedir}/{aid}.html', '{typedir}/index.html', 'default', '', '', '', 0, '{cmspath}/about', '', 0, 0, '', '&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">基本数据</b></span><span style="background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	每月1500万浏览量&nbsp;<br style="word-wrap: break-word;" />\r\n	用户平均浏览页面4.75，平均访问时长18分钟&nbsp;<br style="word-wrap: break-word;" />\r\n	总计20+万 新浪微博、腾讯微博粉丝&nbsp;<br style="word-wrap: break-word;" />\r\n	总计200+万 搜狐新闻客户端、网易云阅读、鲜果等阅读平台订阅用户&nbsp;<br style="word-wrap: break-word;" />\r\n	Alexa：全球排名 1200&mdash;3000，国内排名：100&mdash;&mdash;300</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<br style="word-wrap: break-word;" />\r\n	<span style="word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">本站用户</b></span>&nbsp;<br style="word-wrap: break-word;" />\r\n	男性读者占比79.26%<br style="word-wrap: break-word;" />\r\n	25-49岁用户占比70%&nbsp;<br style="word-wrap: break-word;" />\r\n	75%用户分布北上广、浙江、海外&nbsp;<br style="word-wrap: break-word;" />\r\n	本科以上学历用户占比70%&nbsp;<br style="word-wrap: break-word;" />\r\n	移动设备访问占比30%</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<br style="word-wrap: break-word;" />\r\n	<span style="word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">本站内容渠道</b></span>&nbsp;<br style="word-wrap: break-word;" />\r\n	本站微信公众平台&nbsp;<br style="word-wrap: break-word;" />\r\n	本站APP&nbsp;<br style="word-wrap: break-word;" />\r\n	本站研究报告&nbsp;<br style="word-wrap: break-word;" />\r\n	电子书</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<br style="word-wrap: break-word;" />\r\n	<span style="word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">本站产品及服务</b></span>&nbsp;<br style="word-wrap: break-word;" />\r\n	整合传播&nbsp;<span style="word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em;">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	客户定制会议&nbsp;<br style="word-wrap: break-word;" />\r\n	本站培训</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<br style="word-wrap: break-word;" />\r\n	<span style="word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">本站广告</b></span>&nbsp;<br style="word-wrap: break-word;" />\r\n	站内广告&nbsp;<br style="word-wrap: break-word;" />\r\n	定制化广告&nbsp;<br style="word-wrap: break-word;" />\r\n	微信广告&nbsp;<br style="word-wrap: break-word;" />\r\n	APP广告</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<br style="word-wrap: break-word;" />\r\n	<span style="word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">如果您希望进一步了解本站广告价格，请联系</b></span>：&nbsp;<br style="word-wrap: break-word;" />\r\n	市场合作： 884358@qq.com<br style="word-wrap: break-word;" />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n', '');
INSERT INTO `dede_arctype` (`id`, `reid`, `topid`, `sortrank`, `typename`, `typedir`, `isdefault`, `defaultname`, `issend`, `channeltype`, `maxpage`, `ispart`, `corank`, `tempindex`, `templist`, `temparticle`, `namerule`, `namerule2`, `modname`, `description`, `keywords`, `seotitle`, `moresite`, `sitepath`, `siteurl`, `ishidden`, `cross`, `crossid`, `content`, `smalltypes`) VALUES
(11, 7, 7, 50, '常见问题解答', '{cmspath}/help', 1, 'index.html', 1, 17, -1, 0, 0, '{style}/index_aboutus.htm', '{style}/list_aboutus.htm', '{style}/article_aboutus.htm', '{typedir}/{aid}.html', '{typedir}/index.html', 'default', '', '', '', 0, '{cmspath}/about', '', 0, 0, '', '<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<b style="word-wrap: break-word;"><font size="4" style="word-wrap: break-word;">关于用户账号以及个人中心</font></b></p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<b style="word-wrap: break-word;"><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">Q</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">：非注册浏览与注册浏览有什么区别吗？</span></b></p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">A</b></span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">：</b>本站与其他资讯站点相比的一个特色是：我们提供</span><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">&ldquo;</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">标签订阅</span><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">&rdquo;</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">。而这需要你注册才可以，注册并订阅标签后，我们会根据你的订阅向你的&ldquo;个人中心&rdquo;推送你感兴趣的公司、人物与话题信息。。</span></p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">此外，注册还为了发表真知灼见、插科打诨以及回复别人的真知灼见和插科打诨呀。</span></p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<b style="word-wrap: break-word;"><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">Q</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">：说到</span><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">&ldquo;</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">个人中心</span><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">&rdquo;</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">，那是干嘛的？</span></b></p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">A</b></span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">：</b>那就是</span><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">&ldquo;</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">你的本站</span><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">&rdquo;</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">。在个人中心里，汇聚了你订阅的资讯、你留下的评论、你收藏的文章、你给本站投递发表的文章</span><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">&hellip;&hellip;</span></p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<b style="word-wrap: break-word;"><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">Q</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">：我怎样添加或编辑我的个人信息？</span></b></p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">A</b></span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">：</b>你的个人中心里有个</span><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">&ldquo;</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">设置</span><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">&rdquo;</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">，戳那里就可以啦。</span></p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<b style="word-wrap: break-word;"><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">Q</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">：我能改用户名吗？</span></b></p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">A</b></span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">：</b>亲，用户</span><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">ID</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">是唯一的，改了朋友们就认不出你啦。你如果实在厌烦了某个</span><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">ID</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">，麻烦你只好再用别的邮箱重新注册一个。</span></p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<b style="word-wrap: break-word;"><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">Q</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">：我怎么改密码咧？</span></b></p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">A</b></span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">：</b>考虑到安全，这个问题提得很有前途！也是在设置里呀。本站建议你每隔一段时间更改一下密码。</span></p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">Q：一句话介绍是啥？</b></span></p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">A：</b>您个人品牌的slogan，它将出现在任何本站内容出现的地方。嗅哥提醒你，乱七八糟的广告语可是要被屏蔽的哦。</span></p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<b style="word-wrap: break-word;"><font size="4" style="word-wrap: break-word;">---------------------------------------------------------------------</font></b></p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<b style="word-wrap: break-word;"><font size="4" style="word-wrap: break-word;">关于评论</font></b></p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<b style="word-wrap: break-word;"><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">Q</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">：在本站发言有什么规则？</span></b></p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">A</b></span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">：</b>天朝的明规则就是我们的明规则，天朝的潜规则就是我们的潜规则。你懂的。要是你疏忽了，也请包涵小编不得已刀掉它。</span></p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<b style="word-wrap: break-word;"><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">Q</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">：我为什么被关掉了评论权限？</span></b></p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">A</b></span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">：</b>亲，想必你发言时不小心触发了社会精神文明的和谐机关，冷静</span><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">7</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">天吧。</span></p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<b style="word-wrap: break-word;"><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">Q</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">：我能在评论里加超链接吗？</span></b></p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">A</b></span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">：</b>可以是可以，但系统一旦发现这个链接是小广告或病毒，也会触发和谐机关。</span></p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<b style="word-wrap: break-word;"><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">Q</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">：如果我发现有的评论涉及人身攻击，或者不河蟹，怎么闹？</span></b></p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">A</b></span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">：</b>投诉它，找大虎！</span></p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<b style="word-wrap: break-word;"><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">Q</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">：文末结尾的喜欢、分享和收藏是干嘛用的？</span></b></p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">A</b></span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;"><b style="word-wrap: break-word;">：</b>文章之间也在靠获得的</span><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">&ldquo;</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">喜欢</span><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">&rdquo;</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">数量来角逐最受欢迎的文章排名。被</span><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">&ldquo;</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">喜欢</span><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">&rdquo;</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">得越多，排名就越靠前，让越多人看到的机会就越大。你的表态很重要。</span></p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">&ldquo;</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">分享</span><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">&rdquo;</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">功能，允许读者把文章分享到其他互联网平台上。好文共欣赏。</span></p>\r\n<p .="MsoNormal" align="left" style="word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', ''冬青黑体简体中文 w3'', 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 252);">\r\n	<span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">&ldquo;</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">收藏</span><span .="font-family: Tahoma; " lang="EN-US" style="word-wrap: break-word;">&rdquo;</span><span .="font-family: 宋体; " style="word-wrap: break-word;">一篇文章之后，你可以在自己的个人中心页面温习它。</span></p>\r\n', '');
